extends _layout

block vars
  - var pageTitle = 'About'
  - var pageDescription = 'Roman Licursi is a CS student, revenue operations analyst, and systems builder.'
  - var pagePath = 'about'
  - var bodyClass = 'about'

block header
  p.chapter I
  h1#content About

block content

  .container
    .content
      p Hey! I'm Roman. I'm a CS junior at UW-Madison who thinks in systems and builds things that scale.

      p I care about revenue operations, GTM systems, and using AI as leverage — combining technical depth with business judgment to create measurable impact.

      p I have hands-on experience in outbound operations and GTM strategy through CAUHEC Connect, and I'm headed to Donaldson as a Revenue Operations intern in summer 2026.

      p Right now I'm spending a semester in Prague, building tools, writing, and figuring out what high-leverage work looks like at the intersection of software and go-to-market.

      p I'm a big fan of Naval Ravikant, systems thinking, and work that compounds.
